---
title: Homemade Cheddar, Mustard and Lemon Fishcakes with Peas, Apple Salad and Garlic Aioli
description: Making fish cakes is easier than you think! Flavoured with cheese, mustard and lemon and paired with cod, salmon and smoked haddock, these are paired with peas, apple salad and homemade garlic aioli for a flavoursome dinner.
